  ('medical-tech-moex-14894', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-099-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '有些革蘭氏陰性球桿狀細菌（如Kingella denitrificans）可在淋菌的選擇性培養基上生長，且形態不 易與淋菌區分，下列方法何者有助於判定其為桿菌或球菌？', '["操作penicillin disk test，取抑制圈邊緣生長菌染色觀察", "操作tetracycline disk test，取抑制圈邊緣生長菌染色觀察", "操作vancomycin及colistin感受性試驗", "改用modified Gram-stain"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "671eb858dffa", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "104", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 63, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
